ish-speaking world, mostly among immigrants from Germanic countries."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Otto von Lobdeburg von Alerheim Graf was born in 1132 as the son of Hartmann von Alerheim and Mrs. Mrs. Hartmann. He had at least 1 son with N. von Querfurt."},"et":{"1132–":"1132–Surnud","1132–Male":"1132–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227":"1227","1105":"1105","1213":"1213","1133":"1133","1132":"1132","1162":"1162","1180":"1180"},"fi":{"1132–":"1132–Kuollut","1132–Male":"1132–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227":"1227","1105":"1105","1213":"1213","1133":"1133","1132":"1132","1162":"1162","1180":"1180"},"fr":{"1132–":"1132–Décédé","1132–Male":"1132–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227":"1227","1105":"1105","1213":"1213","1133":"1133","1132":"1132","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","lifeSummary":"Otto von Lobdeburg von Alerheim Graf est né en 1132, fils de Hartmann von Alerheim et Mrs. Mrs. Hartmann. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec N. von Querfurt."},"de":{"1132–":"1132–Verstorben","1132–Male":"1132–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227":"1227","1105":"1105","1213":"1213","1133":"1133","1132":"1132","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","lifeSummary":"Otto von Lobdeburg von Alerheim Graf wurde 1132, als Sohn von Hartmann von Alerheim und Mrs. Mrs. Hartmann geboren. Er hatte mit N. von Querfurt mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1132–":"1132–Desede","1132–Male":"1132–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227":"1227","1105":"1105","1213":"1213","1133":"1133","1132":"1132","1162":"1162","1180":"1180"},"hu":{"1132–":"1132–elhunyt","1132–Male":"1132–elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","1162–1227":"1162–1227","1180–1213":"1180–1213","1105–1133":"1105–1133","1227"